query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND kt.kind in ('movie','tv movie','video movie','video game','episode','tv mini series') AND cct2.kind in ('cast','complete+verified','complete') AND (chn.name like '%Gamora%') AND (t.title like '%mirror%' OR t.title like '%sword%' OR t.title like '%letter%' OR t.title like '%man%') AND t.production_year > 1990 AND it2.info not in ('LD number of sides','top 250 rank','LD number','screenplay-teleplay','votes distribution','LD sharpness','biographical movies','LD disc size','soundtrack','birth date','mini biography','LD catalog number','LD number of chapter stops','color info','where now','LD video artifacts') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','crew','complete+verified')
